<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idb6a4d68c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idb6a4d68d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective as if enacted on <date date="2009-09-30">Sept. 30, 2009</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/111/87/s2/a/3/B">section 2(a)(3)(B) of Pub. L. 111–87</ref>, set out as an Effective Date of 2009 Amendment; Revival of Section note under <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s300ff–11">section 300ff–11 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
